{"tid":2311863,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［黃色文創圈］同大家介紹個講電影同歷史嘅高質Channel","createTime":"2020-12-04T11:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T06:19:55.000Z","uid":188515,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"dd855f34d832c984a8da110d42e0eda5abeb87a8","tid":2311863,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:32:11.000Z","msg":"話說有同路人好用心咁整左唔同嘅片<br />\n透過電影去講唔同嘅歷史同文化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又或者單純探討歷史事件<br />\n希望提高大家嘅歷史意識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時等我地可以用作為借鏡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8SMxiYK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8SMxiYK.png&h=6935be7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［電影與現實］系列<br />\n透過香港電影《同囚》<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n探討香港嘅懲教制度同背後嘅意義<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OtIjcydLiTI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOtIjcydLiTI&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=0bcacf48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OtIjcydLiTI</a> <br />\n<br />\n透過英國電影《黑暗對峙》<br />\n講當年二戰時期<br />\n英國點樣孤軍奮戰抵抗納粹德國<br />\n寄予香港人堅持到底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/B5PH7XlgFWc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB5PH7XlgFWc&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=5a0cdcd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B5PH7XlgFWc</a> <br />\n<br />\n透過韓國電影《南營洞1985》<br />\n揭示80年代嘅韓國獨裁政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點樣通過嚴刑迫供打壓民運人士<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6h_GN1FsCAU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6h_GN1FsCAU&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=89a7c700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6h_GN1FsCAU</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［香港人必須要知的歷史］<br />\n回顧79年前嘅「香港保衛戰」<br />\n等大家認識多啲本土歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MrIl8SF8gxY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMrIl8SF8gxY&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=3e3d21df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MrIl8SF8gxY</a> <br />\n<br />\n藉著今年嘅泰國示威<br />\n講下泰國嘅社運歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pfhZPsfDPhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpfhZPsfDPhk&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=7965e13e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pfhZPsfDPhk</a> <br />\n<br />\n回顧一年前嘅理大圍城<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DkPh_NLSERI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDkPh_NLSERI&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=54959036\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DkPh_NLSERI</a> <br />\n<br />\n仲有好多唔同嘅片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣可以㩒入去再睇<br />\n希望大家可以支持下手足cls<br />\n撐起本土文化圈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d21bfeec4ba4f2f81dbb5f52c3d7e1a43d15565","tid":2311863,"uid":188515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:32:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97f1df46132fae7a7eb6da4f0b00af177d8fb0d6","tid":2311863,"uid":188515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:34:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ac74e61e13c4cad5f9795cab742b9045ed46b89","tid":2311863,"uid":188515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7de7c0f4ed1ac2f65c47f5508e79c7555e60e5","tid":2311863,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:10:48.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb7d2b00bc21639ba114916cdb93d9b68d13732","tid":2311863,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:37:52.000Z","msg":"再幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361c33a01c505dac2ef10356be8d62eceb12113e","tid":2311863,"uid":188515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9eb7d2b00bc21639ba114916cdb93d9b68d13732","tid":2311863,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:37:52.000Z","msg":"再幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:46:59.000Z","msg":"沉底底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b6cce7f1041546103696b61772562c44468418f","tid":2311863,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4273183debc7c2d33083156eaaeec72d30ddaa","tid":2311863,"uid":151224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T22:43:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f005f2868a8d72b717f4c4fa85ebb95e500e6d74","tid":2311863,"uid":89030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T00:49:53.000Z","msg":"好難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02c55200509addc24042777e57ab6e63c1390dd","tid":2311863,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T02:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ddb079b0c8dae55fda12b78db33e36dfb34ebe","ti