replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:19:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到呢啲有心又高汁既Channel<br />\n得咁少人睇好心酸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:52:18.000Z","msg":"香港人係好少人有心學習<br />\n<br />\n利申日日聽蕭生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T05:08:09.000Z","msg":"之前有個講黃Youtube channel既post幾好<br />\n早排唔知有咩好睇 逐個禁入去<br />\n都發現左幾多好野<br />\n但望一望啲subscribe數...<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望多啲人發掘下唔同類型既channel啦<br />\nG持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24cff4ae506bca602f43bd5e00d135d7b21c3f14","tid":2311863,"uid":40887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T05:11:55.000Z","msg":"推"}]}